- Has R in position 3.

- Uses only the still-allowed letters.

- “D” is out (already ruled out)
- “N” or “M” or “G” or “Y”, etc.

- R (position 3) – matches ✓  
- R (position 4) – acceptable; we have no info against another R.  
- Y – unused yet.

So “LORRY” seems best.
